is-essay-4850005.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto"/></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-1 bLA-dMf"><div class="sc-d56bc236-8 gArifC"><div class="sc-d56bc236-5 ZcrSZ"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-d56bc236-4 gKlMxC">Save</span></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-3 iOJnhy eIqCxs">essay</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-2 iOJnhy llXHdp">Nations and empires</p></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-10 tdBWn">A United States of Europe</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-11 hYbLtW">A free and unified Europe was first imagined by Italian radicals in the 19th century. Could we yet see their dream made real?</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-12 iOJnhy dFhhBp">Fernanda Gallo</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 kQroYe"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><footer class="sc-8723d312-0 fVfKHB footer" data-test="footer"><div class="sc-ae266dcd-0 sc-8723d312-1 bwTVbW dRXxEN"><div class="sc-1b596d24-0 ithRRD"><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/essays" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Essays</a><a href="/ideas" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Ideas</a><a href="/videos" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Videos</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a h